Class jkp.KifSeq 

java.lang.Object
   |
   +----jkp.KifObj
           |
           +----jkp.KifSeq
public class KifSeq
extends KifObj
The class for KIF object sequence, such as term sequence(in a relational sentence), sentence sequence(in conjuction/disjunction), etc. A very important class in this parser.

Copyright (c) 1996, Xiaocheng Luan. All rights reserved.

Author:
Xiaocheng Luan
